ce/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a division\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbRaygun's revenge\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 219}, {\"ngram\": \"world\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"number\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Olympic breakdancer \\\"Raygun\\\" has been ridiculed, written off, and now crownednumber one in the world, the sport's governing body confirmed on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9698491931787023, \"rank\": 0.02918043372755228, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's governing body\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rachael \\\"Raygun\\\" Gunn, 37, became something of a global laughing stock after her kangaroo-inspired routine failed to impress the judges at theParis Olympics, where the sport of breaking made its debut.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 2.8911281168886768e-12, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.733473035264865e-29, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"a global laughing stock\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"her kangaroo-inspired routine\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"its debut\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her moves were parodied on late-night talk shows, her unfashionable tracksuit was lampooned online and breaking aficionados around the world questioned how she had made the team.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her moves\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"her unfashionable tracksuit\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"aficionados\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Raygun got her revenge and the last laugh when the World Dance Sport Federation (WDSF) named her the number one female breakdancer in the world.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raygun\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"her revenge\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"the last laugh\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Dance Sport Federation\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"the number one female breakdancer\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rankings were based on the athlete's four top performances within the past 12 months, said the WDSF on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rankings\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's four top performances\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"the past 12 months\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, with few ranking events held between December 2023 and the Olympics, \\\"many athletes have only one competition result contributing to their ranking,\\\" a WDSF statement said.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"few ranking events\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"many athletes\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"their ranking\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn won the Oceania Continental Championship in that period, earning her 1000 ranking points.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"score\": 0.9999586554934112, \"rank\": 4.110102200971636e-05, \"text\": \"Oceania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that period\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"her 1000 ranking points\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japanese B-girl Riko's win at the Gold World Series in Hong Kong in December 2023 saw her also awarded 1000 points, but the WDSF said Raygun's event carried more weight, so awarded her the top ranking.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9968844485958461, \"rank\": 0.002143198601934132, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9899438614176085, \"rank\": 0.010158012312970296, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"te