 university lecturer\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"a backlash\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"the wider breakdancing community\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn said she had not expected to do well at the Olympics, but that her record showed she was the best breaker in Australia.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2306, \"end\": 2315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9939352285103874, \"rank\": 0.005906250842719512, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"her record\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"the best breaker\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As soon as I qualified, I was like, oh my gosh, what have I done?\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because I knew that I was going to get beaten, and I knew that people were not going to understand my style and what I was going to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"my style\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I am very sorry for the backlash that the community has experienced, but I can not control how people react.\\\"\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn had previously spoken out against the \\\"pretty devastating\\\" hatred unleashed after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2649, \"end\": 2653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\\"pretty devastating\\\" hatred\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went out there and I had fun.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did take it very seriously.\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked my butt off preparing for the Olympics and I gave my all,\\\" she said in a video message last month.\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my butt\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2830}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"a video message\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While many ridiculed her performance on social media, Gunn won support from others, including her fellow Australian Olympians and Australia's prime minister.\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 3080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2977, \"end\": 2981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 3028, \"end\": 3038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedi